headline: Truist Wealth elevates the digital experience with a new modern, mobile forward investment account and portfolio platform
summary: Truist Wealth, the private wealth business of Truist Financial Corporation (NYSE: TFC), is proud to announce a leap forward in its digital transformation journey, powered by InvestCloud, a global leader in wealth technology focused on delivering more meaningful outcomes for clients. This strategic partnership marks a key moment in Truist Wealth's multi-year investment to deliver a differentiated and client-centric digital experience.

headline: Home Depot ’positioned for continued share gains’ says analyst after meeting
summary: Investing.com -- Following Home Depot’s Investor Day in New York, analysts at Truist wrote that the company remains “positioned for continued share gains,” although broader macro uncertainties mean the timing of an upcycle remains hard to call.

headline: Looking at the Changing Narrative for TTM Technologies After AI and Data Center Momentum
summary: TTM Technologies has seen a modest uptick in its fair value estimate to $77.50 from $76.00 as analysts grow more confident that AI driven demand and data center computing will support stronger long term fundamentals. Slightly higher revenue growth assumptions, now at about 8.11% from roughly 7.80%, are anchored in recent beat and raise quarters and expanding high end PCB capacity that should help capture incremental AI and high speed networking demand. Stay tuned to see how investors can...
